# ==============================================================
# 👁️🔥 TRINETRA REPOSITORY GUARDIAN (Point 12: Super App Standards)
# 100% REAL: No Bloat, No Junk, Pure Performance
# ==============================================================

# Flutter-related (ASLI: Added Build & Tooling ignores)
**/Flutter/ephemeral/
**/Flutter/generated/
**/build/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/.packages
**/pubspec.lock  # Optional, but recommended for library apps
**/ios/Flutter/.last_build_id

# CocoaPods (ASLI: Ensuring Pods are never committed)
**/Pods/
**/Podfile.lock
**/ServiceAccount.json

# Xcode-related (ASLI: Added OS-Junk and State protection)
**/dgph
**/xcuserdata/
**/DerivedData/
**/*.moved-aside
**/*.mode1v3
**/*.mode2v3
**/*.perspectivev3
**/*.xccheckout
**/*.DS_Store

# macOS specific (ASLI: The Hidden Traitor)
.DS_Store
**/DerivedData/

# 🔥 EXTRA SECURITY: Secret Keys & Logs
*.log
.env*
